creator: Kinetic-analysis B.V.
descriptionHtml:
This is a free application that you can use to improve your quality of life towards a healthier lifestyle.
The Vital Communities application is the online community of your city. It is a European platform that brings cities and citizens under the same roof, motivating all active members into a more vibrant lifestyle. You and your city contribute to the app's content, bringing new ideas and fun activities live.
You can create your own challenges, events, invite or challenge your friends and family, win points that will benefit you and your city. On top of everything, your actions will lead policymakers to make decisions about the future of your city.
Find out first about the vitality events of your city. Discover valuable articles, videos, and tips about a healthy lifestyle from elite athletes, professional nutritionists, lifestyle coaches to inspire you and promote a healthier and happier way of being.

The VCC App can collect your data when you run, climbing stairs, walking or cycling from your Apple Health, Fitbit, Strava, Garmin, Google, all into one place.
You can find all vitality happenings announced from your city on the app feed, and you can create and see your own challenges and events.

Download and spread the word. You are the contributor of the app; make it extraordinary.
